{"tid":351712,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"可恥 真正借貓上位KOL 出書 扮愛貓","createTime":"2017-08-08T09:30:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-13T22:30:44.000Z","uid":81850,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a1c14869f1fa514dbc0bc158514964bf731d65f9","tid":351712,"uid":81850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T09:30:45.000Z","msg":"點解唔見有巴絲屌真正借貓上位既KOL<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身對呢位KOL都冇咩特別感覺<br />\n係書展出書 話會將收益扣除成本後全數撥捐非牟利的流浪動物協會<br />\n都覺得雖然都係利用啲貓貓 但都叫做幫到人 做下善事<br />\n點知直到見到呢段<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/08/170131_c1110f63728cb946abaae0714cd6f5f9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F08%2F170131_c1110f63728cb946abaae0714cd6f5f9.jpg&h=b365ffa6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n為左幫本書做宣傳 可以帶隻貓出去見fans<br />\n正常都唔會帶貓出街 就算係出都係散下步哂下太陽<br />\n但佢帶隻貓去見fans<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去啲咁多人既地方 又講帶隻貓出黎有咩規矩要遵守<br />\n真正愛貓既 為咩要冒咁大風險<br />\n登隻貓可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見咁多人 實嚇死佢"},{"pid":"c9ecfca4a59c342525752d29adc6aca0382ed148","tid":351712,"uid":25148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T10:35:18.000Z","msg":"個暗星終於上到位?"},{"pid":"c2deab1ae85d39433e869b959697b4a6dbcbe00f","tid":351712,"uid":81850,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T10:35:28.000Z","msg":"冇人同我一樣覺得好過份咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"401f9d30174a6af6774b36ffb35bb092918d1edb","tid":351712,"uid":15348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T10:36:38.000Z","msg":"暗星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"971d66734be9360838e05e1f747cdd6138a08663","tid":351712,"uid":6589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:58:39.000Z","msg":"自己撈youtube撈唔掂就借貓博收視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52dd9877c8e0ac2f153b7401d1d0f683d6d5c3bf","tid":351712,"uid":69092,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T17:58:47.000Z","msg":"又要用恆仔又要用貓上位暗星撈得好辛苦架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Btw電競節關佢咩事？佢有打機？<br />\n利申：一條暗星片都無睇過"},{"pid":"4d5260093fccd322143ebc82eab4f2d5af6e99e9","tid":351712,"uid":67844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T06:40:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔見有巴絲屌真正借貓上位既KOL<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為無睇佢d片"},{"pid":"01848cad5ea798a3a9d829b8291866dfff57d1a7","tid":351712,"uid":67844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T06:40:52.000Z","msg":"佢隻貓真係好慘"},{"pid":"84bb1ac6b5902537b499066f93bf820c3cd6f3a4","tid":351712,"uid":69602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T06:41:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解唔見有巴絲屌真正借貓上位既KOL<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為無睇佢d片</blockquote>"},{"pid":"c8d6dac13e5bafca3707880e0a3522afe3b39eb8","tid":351712,"uid":2059,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T01:51:20.000Z","msg":"屌 痕仔幾時先飛佢呀"},{"pid":"84a2da28518e89a06b26672bb810a8b5b135d96e","tid":351712,"uid":70583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T01:53:46.000Z","msg":"又嚟愈屌愈紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c32989c6ed5bf68e855c104c8209778ebeb9290b","tid":351712,"uid":72228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T01:55:08.000Z","msg":"暗星真係好撚柒"},{"pid":"2da3be4dc41e3287a1937951421fdbec4b16b2d7","tid":351712,"uid":77569,"like":0,"dis